<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Hey - it's that guy, Isaac!</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <!-- Le HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML elements -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <![endif]-->

    <!-- Le styles -->
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
    <style>
      body {
        padding-top: 60px; /* 60px to make the container go all the way to the bottom of the topbar */
      }
    </style>

    <!-- Le fav and touch icons -->
    <link href="images/favicon.ico" rel="shortcut icon">
    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon">
    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon-72x72.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="72x72">
    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon-114x114.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="114x114">
  </head>
<body>

    <div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="navbar-inner">
        <div class="container">
          <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".nav-collapse">
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </a>
          <a class="brand" href="<%= root_path %>">Isaac Elias</a>
          <div class="nav-collapse">
            <ul class="nav">
              <li class="active"><%= link_to "Welcome", root_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "Education", education_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "Experience", experience_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "Professional Interests", prof_in_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "Personal Interests", pers_in_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "Contact", contact_path %></li>
            </ul>
          </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>

        <div class="container">

      <!-- Main hero unit for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span4">
            <ul class="thumbnails">
              <li class="span4">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                  <img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-KPtKgpb8kms/TXRMx09QLzI/AAAAAAAACno/pXNYyIaCFOo/s400/06172009337.jpg" alt="">
                 <!-- <h5></h5> -->
                  
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="span6">
            <h1>Who's this?!</h1>
            <p>For some reason&mdash;unbeknownst to yours truly&mdash;you have chosen to seek out some information about one <strong>"Isaac Elias"</strong>. I hope you found the right one; if not, I know of a good <%= link_to "search engine", "http://www.google.com/search?q=%22Isaac+Elias%22" %>. </p>
            <p>Feel free to use the buttons across the top of this page to get to know more about me. One of the first things you should know is that I'm a people person, and acccordingly, I'd be thrilled to make your acquaintence! So use the yellow button if you'd like to - 
            <a href="<%= contact_path %>" class="btn btn-warning btn-large">Get in touch &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>

      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <div class="row"> <p style="text-align:justify"><h1>So, tell me about you&mdash;are you ...</h1></p>
        <div class="span4">
          <h2>Hiring?</h2>
           <p>I'm graduating with a B.S. in Business Administration this May! I love marketing and social media - and went to Iraq and Afhganistan while in the U.S. Army. Please check out my - </p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="<%= education_path %>">Education page &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h2>A new internet friend?</h2>
           <p>Maybe I asked a dumb question on <%= link_to "Hacker News", "http://news.ycombinator.com/"%> or <%= link_to "Stack Overflow", "http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/ruby-on-rails-3.1?sort=newest"%>. Maybe someone retweeted <%= link_to "me", "http://twitter.com/brainscraps/" %> by mistake. No matter how you found me, you can get to know me through my -</p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="<%= pers_in_path %>">Personal interests &raquo;</a></p>
       </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h2>Family or close friend?</h2>
          <p>This is the kind of fun thing I get to do while going to <a href="<%= education_path %>">school</a>! Feel free to poke around and learn more about me. If you'd like to make fun of me, give me some feedback on the site, or catch up, please go to the - </p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="<%= contact_path %>">Contact page &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <footer>
        <p>&copy; Isaac Elias, 2012 </p>
      </footer>

    </div> <!-- /container -->


    <!-- Le javascript
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster -->
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>

  </body>
</html>


